g src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c432c58ae089eebdd1c3410d7a695b4f23c263","tid":2398571,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"200461ac700dfbba1accc6f71b381868c37e1f83","tid":2398571,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"留港撚：<br />\n<br />\n我坐成監都要留喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">不論離開定堅守都係手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> </span><br />\n<br />\n決意堅守陣地既手足，必須時刻警惕提防，保留有用之軀，日後方能煲底相見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我認為<span class=\"red\">中共已撕破臉皮，唔會再講法理情，更盡一切辦法會趕盡殺絕</span>，本土戰線只餘硬碰硬一著，而港共武裝與抗爭者實力相距太大，難成氣候，除非把抗爭層面擴大化，將火魔、簡易組裝槍械等等變成家家戶戶都有的必備品，否則難以對抗如同送頭，亦無必要，而且傳播該類資訊係十分頭痛既問題，能參與者的數量亦成疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> 但  <span class=\"red\">今次 BNO 大量港人走資走人不旦只可以保有用之驅全身而退保存實力，更可以逼中共支爆發難，借東風引天下圍中，百國聯軍，打柒老共，核平北京！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>所以：</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins><span class=\"xx-large\"> <span class=\"red\">離開唔係逃避，係主動攬炒救香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>警號已經響起咗！<span class=\"red\">越著時間過去，離開香港將會日漸困難</span>，大時代中不能存有饒幸之心，成日同自己講冇事既、冇事既個d人，就係走唔切，困咗係東德既人。<span class=\"red\">總之任何人，有得即走，特別高風險人士一定要最早走，其他人遲極唔可以遲過外國撤僑，外國第一個國家撤僑你就要跟住飛。外國唔會一次過撤，會比時間同signal香港人走先。</span>切記你係難民唔係移民。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪好好奇美國點解得把口唔出手制裁？我話你知幾時先制裁、有冇可能封關、應唔應該走、幾時要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2093986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2093986</a><br />\n<br />\n(分析)仲有幾耐入東突(新疆)模式，見到咩警告要流亡？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1980175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1980175</a><br />\n<br />\n香港簡易流亡手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/478029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/478029</a><br />\n<br />\n[借古鑑今] 中國因逃亡潮於 1951 年 2 月 15 日鎖關，香港因 BNO 鎖關的憂慮正響歐美之間蔓延！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2390806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2390806</a>"},{"pid":"a2c3c66ea8e6cb5bd31b462cdb86f468a29ece80","tid":2398571,"uid":96909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:56:31.000Z","msg":"上路了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020e8581a6884971948bb350a57023e8a8184071","tid":2398571,"uid":120480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"叫人留港果啲肯定係冚家剷<br />\n自己要留，唔好阻人走"},{"pid":"2fe859fdd2b7f12513162a35742ea544a6fd50ea","tid":2398571,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d376fe206911824f67bf4aedd616237976d189d0","tid":2398571,"uid":234457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2aade8f89eccda9cbffd2ed274b40e600dade5","tid":2398571,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98712321d76f5e146e465470f025452c4bbf3dd6","tid":2398571,"uid":230054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3845aad8470f508215545eb820fbc92c80a8a834","tid":2398571,"uid":249646,"like"